## Edits applied (6) — committed `8a52245` in upwork-agentic-workflow
1. **.claude/agents/media-capture.md** (Output) — require asserting DISTINCT MD5s + `>~50KB` per frame before handoff; blank/dup PNGs (wrong serve root) get looped back. [adherence] (final-ceo, proposal-writer re-run: 4 identical blank PNGs shipped).
2. **.claude/agents/media-capture.md** (Rules) — scripts must be `.mjs` and run with the repo folder as cwd (module-type + local node_modules Playwright resolution). [reuse]
3. **.claude/agents/deploy-test.md** — DOM-dump pass BEFORE writing selectors; note RBAC/card demos use div/card `onClick`, not `<button>`. [adherence]/[tokens] (2 wasted script runs on blind selectors).
4. **.claude/agents/image-analyzer.md** — if manifest is conclusively empty, skip screenshot/vision phase and report empty list. [tokens]
5. **.claude/agents/proposal-writer.md** — dash grep must cover markdown headings/kicker strings too, not only body/title/alt. [adherence]
6. **CLAUDE.md** (new "Local-verify scripts" block) — shared `.mjs` + repo-cwd + distinct-MD5/min-size rule so all local-verify steps inherit it once. [reuse]/[adherence]

## Left for human review (not edited — env/risky/uncertain)
- **Pillow / python-pptx not pre-installed** (image-analyzer, proposal-writer [tokens]/[reuse]): an ENVIRONMENT prerequisite (bake into setup image), not a prompt fix; prompts already say "install once at step start." Needs infra change, out of my scope.
- **image-analyzer: "Read renders JPEG as raw binary; use a PIL crop-to-JPEG workaround"** [reuse]: contradicts the spec's "Read renders the image so you see it" and may be Copilot-runtime-specific. Do not encode a workaround that could be false on Claude Code — verify the tool behavior first.
- **deploy-test: shared serve+Playwright setup module / prerequisite server step** [reuse]: a real refactor of the run harness, not a surgical prompt edit. Design before adopting.

